### Django Blog API Test Requests

@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8000/api

### Get all articles
GET {{baseUrl}}/articles/

### Get specific article
GET {{baseUrl}}/articles/1/

### Create new article
POST {{baseUrl}}/articles/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Test Article from REST Client",
  "content": "This is a test article created using VS Code REST Client extension. It demonstrates how to test POST requests with JSON data.",
  "author": "REST Client User"
}

### Update article (replace 1 with actual article ID)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/articles/1/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Article Title",
  "content": "This article has been updated using the PUT method.",
  "author": "Updated Author"
}

### Delete article (replace 1 with actual article ID)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/articles/1/

### Get article statistics
GET {{baseUrl}}/articles/stats/

### Test with query parameters (filter by author)
GET {{baseUrl}}/articles/?author=Django

### Test pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/articles/?page=1
